text: Anne Kukkohovi (née Laaksonen, born 3 October 1970 in Vaasa) is a retired Finnish model who has worked both in and outside Finland from 1990 to 1998. She currently works as an art director in an advertising agency. Kukkohovi has also been a host on the Finnish television show Sinun unelmiesi tähden at the end of the 1990s. She is currently the host of the Finnish version of America's Next Top Model, Suomen huippumalli haussa.
